odically built to maximize tension and intrigue. What is this place? The facility just keeps going down and down. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you going to find any answers once you reach the bottom?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002510/extras/description03.png?t=1738719026\" /></p>","developers":["Boz\u00f3 Attila Bertold"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002510/header.jpg?t=1738719026","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"\u00a92024 Boz\u00f3 Attila Bertold<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures soundtrack composed and performed by:<br />\r\nOur Star Is Dying<br />\r\nTom Jensen","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257092557,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257092557/movie480.mp4?t=1738083512","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257092557/movie_max.mp4?t=1738083512"},"name":"REPOSE | Publisher Reveal","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257092557/803b2ac8b22b974ccebc601ab4cf7f16cfcbaa2f/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1738083512","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257092557/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1738083512","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257092557/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1738083512"}}],"name":"REPOSE","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li